{"tid":719411,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"阿根廷換人戰術指揮入球傳送　上帝話晒事","createTime":"2018-06-27T11:47:15.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-27T12:30:47.000Z","uid":20634,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"6fa01a5ebf9b88708532fd327d89f869db5f199c","tid":719411,"uid":20634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T11:47:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://images-sports.now.com/sport/news/2/232/21948572232/21955134245_600x399.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages-sports.now.com%2Fsport%2Fnews%2F2%2F232%2F21948572232%2F21955134245_600x399.jpg&h=3fac03aa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=KEBMhe5rGA8bf52ZRo792cmB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=965761bd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】阿根廷教練森柏奧利名存實亡，據報他已手持換人大權，而馬高斯盧祖大爆隊長「半場訓話」。<br />\n<br />\n阿根廷主帥森柏奧利似乎真的已有名無實，當周二對尼日利亞比數仍是1:1時，被鏡頭拍到上前向美斯（Lionel Messi）發問「我應否換入阿古路」，完全失去執教權力。該場世界盃D組賽，阿根廷終險勝尼日利亞2:1，神奇次名晉級16強，箇中很多細節值得回味。<br />\n<br />\n後衛馬高斯盧祖（Marcos Rojo）大爆，下半場回到球場時，隊長美斯在球場上的訓話內容。「他叫我們要冷靜、專注，每個人都有入波責任，只要有機會就起腳。」<br />\n<br />\n盧祖最後成為贏波功臣，絕殺超霸鷹，他解說當時的心思：「當皮球飛過來時，我就射門，美斯的說給對我們幫助很大，<span style=\"color: red;\">他是世界上最佳的隊長</span>。」"},{"pid":"f3e48df05f1af4723000180a5b4de72235e75b5f","tid":719411,"uid":53238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T12:15:09.000Z","msg":"球員兼教練 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40a8925bee0829e4ea646de841b9fa84f6d37795","tid":719411,"uid":60668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T12:25:29.000Z","msg":"gabi 好得意 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45874b364883ec23136fdb341abfe7e418e28bac","tid":719411,"uid":49144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T12:30:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}